Kanji Keywords: Heisig 5th Edition vs. jpdb.io

This comparison table shows the kanji keywords for Heisig's Remembering the Kanji, 5th Edition, and jpdb.io (as of April 2025).

Possible keyword conflicts are indicated in parentheses, with RtK 3 kanji in a lighter color. In order to catch as many possible conflicts as possible, we use the stem of the keyword for comparison, but note that it is not 100% reliable.

You can also download this table as a CSV file.
